headline: Campbell to Divest Its noosa Yogurt Brand to Focus on Core Business
summary: CPB announces the sale of the noosa yogurt brand to focus on core brands, aiding growth in fiscal 2025.

headline: TreeHouse Foods Q3 Earnings Meet, View Cut on Weak Consumption Trends
summary: THS Q3 results show top-line pressures from the voluntary griddle recall and lower volume/mix, with significant margin improvements and y/y bottom-line growth.
